### ========================================
### Lixian.Online API - REST Client 示例
### ========================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000


### ========================================
### VSCode
### ========================================

### 1. 查询插件版本
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/vscode/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filters": [
    {
      "criteria": [
        {
          "filterType": 7,
          "value": "anthropic.claude-code"
        }
      ],
      "pageNumber": 1,
      "pageSize": 1,
      "sortBy": 0,
      "sortOrder": 0
    }
  ],
  "flags": 1
}

### 2. 直接下载 VSIX（最终文件不走本站代理）
# GET https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/_apis/public/gallery/publishers/anthropic/vsextensions/claude-code/1.2.3/vspackage


### ========================================
### Chrome
### ========================================

### 3. 搜索扩展
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chrome/search?q=ublock

### 4. 获取扩展详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chrome/detail?id=cjpalhdlnbpafiamejdnhcphjbkeiagm

### 5. 下载 CRX
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chrome/download?id=cjpalhdlnbpafiamejdnhcphjbkeiagm


### ========================================
### Microsoft Edge
### ========================================

### 6. 搜索扩展
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/edge/search?q=ublock

### 7. 通过 CRX ID 获取扩展详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/edge/detail?query=cimighlppcgcoapaliogpjjdehbnofhn

### 8. 通过 ProductId 获取扩展详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/edge/detail?query=0RDCK9JPHJM1

### 9. 通过商店 URL 获取扩展详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/edge/detail?query=https%3A%2F%2Fmicrosoftedge.microsoft.com%2Faddons%2Fdetail%2Fublock-origin-lite%2Fcimighlppcgcoapaliogpjjdehbnofhn

### 10. 下载 CRX
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/edge/download?id=cimighlppcgcoapaliogpjjdehbnofhn


### ========================================
### Docker
### ========================================

### 11. 获取标签
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/docker/tags?namespace=library&repository=nginx

### 12. 获取匿名 token
# @name dockerAuth
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/docker/auth?namespace=library&repository=nginx

### 13. 获取 manifest（依赖上一步 token）
@dockerToken = {{dockerAuth.response.body.token}}
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/docker/manifest?namespace=library&repository=nginx&tag=latest&token={{dockerToken}}

### 14. 下载 layer（digest 需替换成 manifest 返回的 layers[].digest）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/docker/layer?namespace=library&repository=nginx&digest=sha256:replace-me&token={{dockerToken}}

### 15. 搜索候选镜像
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/docker/search?q=redis&page_size=5


### ========================================
### Microsoft Store
### ========================================

### 16. 通过商店 URL 解析
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/msstore/resolve?type=url&query=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.microsoft.com%2Fdetail%2F9N0DX20HK701&market=US&language=en-us

### 17. 通过 ProductId 解析
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/msstore/resolve?type=ProductId&query=9N0DX20HK701&market=US&language=en-us

### 18. 通过 PackageFamilyName 解析
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/msstore/resolve?type=PackageFamilyName&query=Microsoft.WindowsTerminal_8wekyb3d8bbwe&market=US&language=en-us

### 19. 通过 CategoryId 解析
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/msstore/resolve?type=CategoryId&query=858014f3-3934-4abe-8078-4aa193e74ca8&market=US&language=en-us

### 20. 代理 HTTP 下载链接
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/msstore/download?url=http%3A%2F%2Ftlu.dl.delivery.mp.microsoft.com%2Ffilestreamingservice%2Ffiles%2Fsample-msix&filename=WindowsTerminal.msixbundle


### ========================================
### 错误用例
### ========================================

### Docker tags - 缺少 repository -> 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/docker/tags?namespace=library

### Docker manifest - 缺少 token -> 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/docker/manifest?namespace=library&repository=nginx&tag=latest

### Chrome download - 无效 ID -> 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chrome/download?id=invalid

### Edge detail - 缺少 query -> 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/edge/detail

### Edge download - 无效 ID -> 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/edge/download?id=invalid

### Chrome search - 缺少关键词 -> 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chrome/search

### MSStore resolve - 缺少 query -> 404 或 500（取决于当前上游返回）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/msstore/resolve?type=ProductId

### MSStore download - 非 HTTP 链接 -> 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/msstore/download?url=https%3A%2F%2Fexample.com%2Ffile.msix
